    public class MazeEditor
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.MouseListener, MazeGame
    MazeEditor - graphical with sprites. Cells are chosen by looping through a list of possible cells (hero, wall, etc.), with mouse clicks in the cell.
